{"tid":231224,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左就會發現世上只有爸媽好","createTime":"2017-05-06T01:14:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-06T01:45:09.000Z","uid":4596,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"05f576e6d4cc3ca8097a8bff77d0e7655839901a","tid":231224,"uid":4596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:14:23.000Z","msg":"終於明白呢個世界上係得老豆老母先會咁無條件咁愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說小弟我今日讀書讀到好大壓力,多嘢讀到就快喊出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但呢個時候香港嗰邊嘅人全部瞓晒覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 冇朋友可以傾訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁我就試吓打俾阿媽,阿媽即刻好緊張咁問我咩事,我即刻喊晒咁同佢講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 跟住阿媽講住一個鐘嘅鼓勵說話嚟鼓勵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲話就算我成績唔好佢同老豆都係咁愛我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老豆返夜班放工之後又skype我同我講話就算我defer佢都會繼續供我讀書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰一刻真係喊出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當然最愛嘅仲有細妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 家人我愛你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"298e9bde780b68a2be5eeec467de072efe0390f1","tid":231224,"uid":46609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:28:55.000Z","msg":"比心機啦樓主，出黎社會做野仲大壓力"},{"pid":"f553c6a46f93a4c35ec45465062351350d9abdfd","tid":231224,"uid":111522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-06T01:45:09.000Z","msg":"讀書只是人生的一個微細點，既然家人都對你開懷，你就放輕鬆地一步一步行。"}]}